summary: These replacers are just some small mesh conversions of popular outfits found around the Nexus for UNPB BBP.
descriptionHtml:
Currently just a placeholder.

Will update when I am happy with a mesh (no clipping, all weight scales, etc)

There will likely be some issues with clipping, just report such issues, and I'll try and fix it.

All credit goes to original authors, and anyone is free to use these remeshes as they wish, just remember to credit the original authors for their fantastic work.

Cheers.
author: Caveat
